HEADWORD: Prejudical
<hw>Pre*ju"di*cal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to the determination of some matter not previously decided; <as>as, a
<ex>prejudical</ex> inquiry or action at law</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prejudicant</ent>⟦br⟧
